snippet.title: Light From Within NES Game Teaser Trailer!
snippet.description:
Adventure awaits in this new game for your Nintendo Entertainment System!


Play as Eleanor, a young girl lost in a strange land.  Discover secrets, find ancient relics, meet unusual creatures, and plunder dungeons in your search for your missing brother.
